MaildirStore uu-local
SubFolders Verbatim
Path ~/Mail/uu/
Inbox ~/Mail/uu/Inbox

IMAPAccount uu
Host mail.uu.se
User xiach215
PassCmd "secret-tool lookup port imaps user xiach215 host mail.uu.se"
SSLType IMAPS
AuthMechs PLAIN

IMAPStore uu-remote
Account uu

Channel uu
Far :uu-remote:
Near :uu-local:
Patterns "INBOX" "Sent Items" "Deleted Items" "Archive" "Junk Email"
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

MaildirStore vvvu-local
SubFolders Verbatim
Path ~/Mail/vvvu/
Inbox ~/Mail/vvvu/Inbox

IMAPAccount vvvu
Host mail.vvvu.org
User xchen@vvvu.org
PassCmd "secret-tool lookup port imaps user xchen host mail.vvvu.org"
SSLType IMAPS

IMAPStore vvvu-remote
Account vvvu

Channel vvvu
Far :vvvu-remote:
Near :vvvu-local:
Patterns "INBOX" "Sent" "Deleted" "Archive" "Junk"
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *
